### VS Code REST Client Demo for AI Insurance Claims Processing
### To use: Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code, then click "Send Request" below

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Submit Medical Claim (Demo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/submit_claim
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Patient presents with severe chest pain and shortness of breath. ECG shows abnormal rhythm. Doctor recommends immediate cardiac evaluation.",
  "claim_type": "medical",
  "priority": "high"
}

### 3. Submit Suspicious Auto Claim (Fraud Detection Demo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/submit_claim
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Customer claims minor slip and fall but demands $47,935 in damages. Details are vague and inconsistent. No witnesses reported.",
  "claim_type": "auto",
  "priority": "medium"
}

### 4. Get AI Recommendation for Medical Claim
POST {{baseUrl}}/get_recommendation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "claim_id": "demo_medical_001",
  "text": "Patient presents with severe chest pain and shortness of breath. ECG shows abnormal rhythm. Doctor recommends immediate cardiac evaluation.",
  "claim_type": "medical",
  "amount": 15234.67
}

### 5. Search Similar Claims
POST {{baseUrl}}/search_claims
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "chest pain emergency room heart attack",
  "claim_type": "medical",
  "limit": 5
}

### 6. Process a File Upload (if you have files)
POST {{baseUrl}}/process_file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="ER_report.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

